{"tid":754820,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"(歡迎討論，突然諗到)究竟所以new age係咩黎?","createTime":"2018-07-24T16:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T10:34:23.000Z","uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b44e128bd118ed6b8e2c07537b1269cec170407b","tid":754820,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:53:22.000Z","msg":"有班人想得到宗教嘅好處(內心平安、有神保佑、心靈成長，甚至神通)，但係唔想守宗教嘅規矩同修行，所以佢地就喺宗教抽自己想聽嘅野出，話唔啱聽嘅野係廢嘅。例如，世上上冇業力冇分對錯，人人都可以上天堂，天使好容易召喚...<br />\n<br />\n自己去過學靈氣，咩都feel唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa8b51d321bae3ad790a8361caf1507cad90bfb","tid":754820,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"究竟同所以唔可以一齊用"},{"pid":"aa37385bd6812bae468eb28876163a35f0415c7f","tid":754820,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa8b51d321bae3ad790a8361caf1507cad90bfb","tid":754820,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"究竟同所以唔可以一齊用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"原來想打所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d498560bf2f1eeea89cc99861d7039f0985d293","tid":754820,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"一群F F愛好者？"},{"pid":"41b8f747f3ce2565355981d1d0ac1abbc0671f87","tid":754820,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"其實主要係某些宗教太唔合理（例如，基督教信者得救，不信永下地獄） <br />\n<br />\n但又唔想做無神論/不可知論者，又要信有神，有鬼，有靈魂，信來世和天堂，又唔改信傳統佛教或道教 <br />\n<br />\nnew age 咪滿足到"}]}